INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('140', '1', '2015-01-25 16:40:08', '2015-01-25 16:40:08', '[fullwidth backgroundcolor=\"\" backgroundimage=\"\" backgroundrepeat=\"no-repeat\" backgroundposition=\"left top\" backgroundattachment=\"scroll\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_preview_image=\"\" overlay_color=\"\" overlay_opacity=\"0.5\" video_mute=\"yes\" video_loop=\"yes\" fade=\"no\" bordersize=\"0px\" bordercolor=\"\" borderstyle=\"\" paddingtop=\"20px\" paddingbottom=\"20px\" paddingleft=\"0px\" paddingright=\"0px\" menu_anchor=\"\" equal_height_columns=\"no\" hundred_percent=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"single\" sep_color=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>About Us</strong>[/title][fusion_text]AIM - Our Company\r\n\r\nEstablished in May 2013, AIM Logistic had grown steadily and planning into the South East Asia Region.\r\n\r\nAIM Logistics provides Cross Border Trucking as our core business within the region of Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Laos, Vietnam, Cambodia and China.\r\n\r\nWith our global networks with the respective affiliated partners, AIM Logistics is able to provide its customers fast, reliable services on a one stop solution without complication.\r\n\r\nWith our Aspire and Innovative Management Team, we also position ourselves with customer to meet the current competition in the region to gain values for both interest.\r\n\r\nAIM - Our Commitment\r\n\r\nWe aspire to fulfil our services render to our value customers and stay focus in the region to meet standards and requirement\r\n\r\nAlways seek innovative to enhance our value and position in the region.\r\n\r\nManagement concept to maintain our services and continuous improvement on our services.\r\n\r\nPartnership working environment with our value customer to seek break through of the logistics environment.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"\" bottom_margin=\"\" sep_color=\"\" icon=\"\" width=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][imageframe lightbox=\"no\" style_type=\"none\" bordercolor=\"\" bordersize=\"0px\" borderradius=\"0\" stylecolor=\"\" align=\"center\" link=\"\" linktarget=\"_self\" animation_type=\"0\" animation_direction=\"down\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"] <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://catchway.org/sg/aimlogistics.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/background_main.png\" />[/imageframe][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"\" bottom_margin=\"\" sep_color=\"\" icon=\"\" width=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]<strong>AIM - Our Company Resources:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Singapore Office</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Company Strength: 4 Staffs</li>\r\n	<li>Truck: 2 x 24ft Trucks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Malaysia Office</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Company Strength: 8 Staffs</li>\r\n	<li>Truck: 30 x 40ft Trucks (Affiliated Partner)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][/fullwidth]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '38-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-25 16:40:08', '2015-01-25 16:40:08', '', '38', 'http://aimlogistics.com.sg/38-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('45', '1', '2014-12-27 06:43:10', '2014-12-27 06:43:10', '[fullwidth backgroundcolor=\"\" backgroundimage=\"\" backgroundrepeat=\"no-repeat\" backgroundposition=\"left top\" backgroundattachment=\"scroll\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_preview_image=\"\" overlay_color=\"\" overlay_opacity=\"0.5\" video_mute=\"yes\" video_loop=\"yes\" fade=\"no\" bordersize=\"0px\" bordercolor=\"\" borderstyle=\"\" paddingtop=\"20px\" paddingbottom=\"20px\" paddingleft=\"0px\" paddingright=\"0px\" menu_anchor=\"\" equal_height_columns=\"no\" hundred_percent=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"single\" sep_color=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>About Us</strong>[/title][fusion_text]Ever in the pursuit for excellence, Aim Logistics strives to bridge the void between you and the global arena. Capitalizing on its in-depth domain knowledge and expertise in the field, the organization grew from a mere logistics solutions provider to a diverse business conglomerate, which now is parent to various companies that offer a plethora of services. With the passage of time, the organization has built for itself a extensive portfolio of clients, which include both multinationals as well as blue-chip corporates worldwide.\r\n\r\nInitiated under the label Aim Logistics in the early 1990s, as a company, offered logistics and supply chain management services. The group now prides itself of being Singapore\'s only leading multi-modal logistics company with single-window integrated logistics services covering all of the elements of supply chain management.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;[/fusion_text][imageframe lightbox=\"no\" style_type=\"none\" bordercolor=\"\" bordersize=\"0px\" borderradius=\"0\" stylecolor=\"\" align=\"none\" link=\"\" linktarget=\"_self\" animation_type=\"0\" animation_direction=\"down\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"] <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://catchway.org/sg/aimlogistics.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/background_main.png\" />[/imageframe][fusion_text]It pioneered 3PL—with a specific focus on inbound cargo for OEMs—with permutations and combinations of Just in Time and Direct Online deliveries, and is a proud leading manager in efficient handling of Surface, Sea, Express, Train, and Air Cargo services.\r\n\r\nApart from its prowess as a complete logistics solutions provider, Aim Logistics, with a turnover of 1000 cr,as a conglomerate, owns expert organizations that offer a gamut of services, which they themselves specialize in, taking the organization’s competence to handle varied tasks to an entirely new level. This competence is spread across fields such as Auto, Telecom, and Consumer Goods, which caters to the complete supply chain, beginning from sourcing of raw materials to delivering it to the end user; in some cases, even recycling for a cleaner environment. The company also undertakes information management, professionally managing critical documents/information in all forms.[/fusion_text][/fullwidth]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '38-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-27 06:43:10', '2014-12-27 06:43:10', '', '38', 'http://catchway.org/sg/aimlogistics.com.sg/38-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
