pe=\"none\" bordercolor=\"\" bordersize=\"0px\" borderradius=\"0\" stylecolor=\"\" align=\"center\" link=\"\" linktarget=\"_self\" animation_type=\"0\" animation_direction=\"up\" animation_speed=\"1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"] <img src=\"http://catchway.org/sg/aimlogistics.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/company_profile2-300x167.jpg\" alt=\"\" />[/imageframe][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"18\" bottom_margin=\"\" sep_color=\"\" icon=\"\" width=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"3\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"single\" sep_color=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>Fright Forwarding</strong>[/title][fusion_text]Aim Logistics is a full-service domestic and international freight forwarder with over 50 offices worldwide. From complex projects to home deliveries...[/fusion_text][/one_fourth][one_fourth last=\"no\" spacing=\"yes\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][imageframe lightbox=\"yes\" style_type=\"none\" bordercolor=\"\" bordersize=\"0px\" borderradius=\"0\" stylecolor=\"\" align=\"center\" link=\"\" linktarget=\"_self\" animation_type=\"0\" animation_direction=\"up\" animation_speed=\"1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"] <img src=\"http://catchway.org/sg/aimlogistics.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/company_profile3-300x167.jpg\" alt=\"\" />[/imageframe][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"18\" bottom_margin=\"\" sep_color=\"\" icon=\"\" width=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"3\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"single\" sep_color=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>Express Delivery</strong>[/title][fusion_text]Express Delivery of Bakersfield offers you<span class=\"RedText\">on demand same day express delivery or overnight service anywhere in Singapore and beyond.</span>[/fusion_text][/one_fourth][one_fourth last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][imageframe lightbox=\"yes\" style_type=\"none\" bordercolor=\"\" bordersize=\"0px\" borderradius=\"0\" stylecolor=\"\" align=\"center\" link=\"\" linktarget=\"_self\" animation_type=\"0\" animation_direction=\"up\" animation_speed=\"1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"] <img src=\"http://catchway.org/sg/aimlogistics.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/company_profile4-300x167.jpg\" alt=\"\" />[/imageframe][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"18\" bottom_margin=\"\" sep_color=\"\" icon=\"\" width=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"3\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"single\" sep_color=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>Warehouse Logistic</strong>[/title][fusion_text]<span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Our offered services of </span><span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Warehouse Logistic Service</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"> are widely availed by some of the noticeable companies in the domain.</span>[/fusion_text][/one_fourth][/fullwidth][fullwidth backgroundcolor=\"\" backgroundimage=\"\" backgroundrepeat=\"no-repeat\" backgroundposition=\"left top\" backgroundattachment=\"fixed\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_preview_image=\"\" overlay_color=\"\" overlay_opacity=\"0.5\" video_mute=\"yes\" video_loop=\"yes\" fade=\"no\" bordersize=\"0px\" bordercolor=\"\" borderstyle=\"solid\" paddingtop=\"55px\" paddingbottom=\"0px\" paddingleft=\"0px\" paddingright=\"0px\" menu_anchor=\"\" equal_height_columns=\"no\" hundred_percent=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][tagline_box backgroundcolor=\"\" shadow=\"no\" shadowopacity=\"0.1\" border=\"1px\" bordercolor=\"\" highlightposition=\"top\" content_alignment=\"left\" link=\"http://themeforest.net/item/avada-responsive-multipurpose-theme/2833226?ref=ThemeFusion\" linktarget=\"_blank\" modal=\"\" button_size=\"large\" button_shape=\"square\" button_type=\"flat\" buttoncolor=\"\" button=\"Send Enquiry\" title=\"Aim Logistics align ourselves as true partners with our customers, collectively driven to reducing expense\" description=\"With a combined team of logistics and IT professionals who share extensive expertise in the industry...\" animation_type=\"0\" animation_direction=\"down\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][/tagline_box][fusion_text][tracking-form][/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"-40\" bottom_margin=\"\" sep_color=\"\" icon=\"\" width=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][one_half last=\"no\" spacing=\"yes\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][accordian class=\"\" id=\"\"][toggle title=\"AIR AND SEA FREIGHT\" open=\"yes\"]As a comprehensive Air and Sea International forwarding and customs brokerage service provider, we offer global services to importers and exporters as well as to assist them in logistic solution. In addition, we have a professional team of staff with notable networking skills and an international freight forwarding networks that strive to maximize customer satisfaction.[/toggle][toggle title=\"LOGISTICS SERVICES &amp; WAREHOUSING\" open=\"no\"]We are one-stop logistic provider that is able to provide full assist to customers’ tailored specific needs. Our logistics expertises are ready to help and meet customers\' transportation requirements. Furthermore, with our spread networks, we are able to cover many destinations.\r\n\r\nWhether transportation is within or across country, customers are assured to have their cargos delivered to the right destination and in order. Pickup services are also provided to serve our customers better.[/toggle][toggle title=\"INTERNATIONAL / LOCAL RELOCATION\" open=\"no\"]Just when you\'ve finally found a place you can call home, the kids are happily fitting into school, and your family\'s comfortably settled down, you\'re faced with the dreaded task of having to relocate. Again. At Aim Logistics, we can help ease the hassles of relocating, so uprooting needn\'t be as traumatic for your family.\r\n\r\nEach move are carefully planned and tailored in accordance to each individual’s requirements and needs. We do offer warehousing space in a clean environment to temporary store the goods for a period of time. [/toggle][/accordian][/one_half][one_half last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text][tabs tab1=\"Profile\" tab2=\"Services\" tab3=\"Experience\"]\r\n\r\n[tab id=1] Our services include a full factory relocation service, international and domestic air, sea and ground transport, packaging, crating, machinery rigging, project management, and other value added services to meet the specific needs of each customer. We are represented in major markets worldwide, allowing us to provide a door-to-door service to and from anywhere in the world.\r\n\r\nIn order to be fully competitive in the international market today, heavy emphasis is placed on solving intricate logistical problems, such as making the timely deliveries to overseas clientele in the most economical and efficient management.\r\n\r\n[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab id=2]\r\n\r\nOur competitive advantage rests on our ability to intimately understand and anticipate our customers\' needs and provide tailored solutions to their relocation and machinery movement requirements by providing the highest levels of the following:\r\n<ul class=\"fl two-width arrow-list\">\r\n	<li>Integrity</li>\r\n	<li>Professionalism</li>\r\n	<li>Dedication</li>\r\n	<li>Reliability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"fl arrow-list\">\r\n	<li>24/7 Accessibility</li>\r\n	<li>Gobal Coverage</li>\r\n	<li>High-tech machinery specialisation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab id=3]\r\n\r\nWe manage and participate in facility ramp-ups, closures, and relocations, moving capital equipment to new locations, new owners, or into storage.\r\n\r\nAim Logistics partners strategically with Singapore-based IES for ion implant relocation projects, as well as other equipment liquidations or relocations that require engineering management and expertise, such as de-installation or re-installation.\r\n\r\n[/tab] [/tabs][/fusion_text][/one_half][/fullwidth][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"0\" bottom_margin=\"\" sep_color=\"\" icon=\"\" width=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-01 11:14:11', '2015-01-01 11:14:11', '', '6', 'http://catchway.org/sg/aimlogistics.com.sg/6-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
