ment\r\n\r\nAlways seek innovative to enhance our value and position in the region.\r\n\r\nManagement concept to maintain our services and continuous improvement on our services.\r\n\r\nPartnership working environment with our value customer to seek break through of the logistics environment.[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"\" bottom_margin=\"\" sep_color=\"\" icon=\"\" width=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"\" bottom_margin=\"\" sep_color=\"\" icon=\"\" width=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]<strong>AIM - Our Company Resources:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Singapore Office</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Company Strength: 4 Staffs</li>\r\n	<li>Truck: 2 x 24ft Trucks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Malaysia Office</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Company Strength: 8 Staffs</li>\r\n	<li>Truck: 30 x 40ft Trucks (Affiliated Partner)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][/fullwidth]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '38-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-17 07:46:49', '2015-02-17 07:46:49', '', '38', 'http://aimlogistics.com.sg/38-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
